stopLossPrice.description:
Before calling this tool, get Last Price from "get_strategy" tool.
Send null to remove stop loss price.

Exact stop loss trigger price (> 0), e.g. 100.55; 
LONG trade range: (0; Last Price); 
SHORT trade range: (Last Price; +Inf)

stopLossMovePrice.description:
Cannot be null when stopLossMoveExecutePrice provided!
Send null to remove stopLossMovePrice.

Move to break-even trigger strict price (>0), e.g. 125.67; 
LONG trade range: (Entry Price; +Inf); 
SHORT trade range: (0; Entry Price)

stopLossMoveExecutePrice.description:
stopLossMovePrice must be defined!
Send null to remove stopLossMoveExecutePrice.

Move to break-even strict price (>0), e.g. 124.5; 
LONG trade range: (0; stopLossMovePrice); 
SHORT trade range: (stopLossMovePrice; +Inf);

extraOrderDeviation.description:
DCA: price deviation (0.001–0.2), equals (0.1% - 20%); Accepts formats like 0.6 or 6%; 
Only for strategyGroupType = dca;

Send null to remove extraOrderDeviation

